      "para_id": "Q001122.2",
      "line_range": "2",
      "translation": "(i 1') ... of Lagaš , šhosen by Nanše in the hearṭ entrusted with the lofty sšeptre by Ninĝirsu , the šhild born by Bau , ..."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001122.11",
      "line_range": "11",
      "translation": "(ii 1') ... of Lagaš , erešted a stela for for Ninĝirsu , his master who loves him , and named it \" Ninĝirsu , the lord , is eternally eₓalted in Nibru \" for him ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001122.20",
      "line_range": "20",
      "translation": "(iii 1') ... fashioned his ( own ) statue , named him \" Lugal-Anda-nuhuĝa is never tired of šaring for Ĝirnun \", ...."
    },
    {
